{%- comment -%}
  KHAN asterisk — the brand's 8-petal radial mark (3rd mark, alongside wordmark + skull).
  Colour = blood fill (.khan-asterisk) with a vivid red outline that gives the "lit" quality.
  Size via a modifier class passed in `class` (khan-asterisk--xs|sm|md|lg).
  TODO(krasi): replace placeholder petal geometry with the official Figma asterisk export.
  Usage: {%- render 'khan-asterisk', class: 'khan-asterisk--md' -%}
{%- endcomment -%}
<span class="khan-asterisk {{ class }}" aria-hidden="true">
  <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
    <g stroke="#e63946" stroke-width="0.4" stroke-linejoin="round">
      <path d="M12 12 C12.7 7 12.4 3.5 12 1.5 C11.6 3.5 11.3 7 12 12 Z"/>
      <path d="M12 12 C12.7 7 12.4 3.5 12 1.5 C11.6 3.5 11.3 7 12 12 Z" transform="rotate(45 12 12)"/>
      <path d="M12 12 C12.7 7 12.4 3.5 12 1.5 C11.6 3.5 11.3 7 12 12 Z" transform="rotate(90 12 12)"/>
      <path d="M12 12 C12.7 7 12.4 3.5 12 1.5 C11.6 3.5 11.3 7 12 12 Z" transform="rotate(135 12 12)"/>
      <path d="M12 12 C12.7 7 12.4 3.5 12 1.5 C11.6 3.5 11.3 7 12 12 Z" transform="rotate(180 12 12)"/>
      <path d="M12 12 C12.7 7 12.4 3.5 12 1.5 C11.6 3.5 11.3 7 12 12 Z" transform="rotate(225 12 12)"/>
      <path d="M12 12 C12.7 7 12.4 3.5 12 1.5 C11.6 3.5 11.3 7 12 12 Z" transform="rotate(270 12 12)"/>
      <path d="M12 12 C12.7 7 12.4 3.5 12 1.5 C11.6 3.5 11.3 7 12 12 Z" transform="rotate(315 12 12)"/>
    </g>
  </svg>
</span>
